---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ParallaxBanner from '../../components/ParallaxBanner.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bulverde Neighborhoods | Cody Posey Real Estate"
  description="Explore Bulverde, TX neighborhoods by community and price range. Find the right fit for your lifestyle and budget in the Hill Country."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="bv-hero">
      <div class="bv-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="bv-hero__content">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/bulverde/">Bulverde</a> <span>/</span> <span>Neighborhoods</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Bulverde <span style="color:#FF1616;">Neighborhoods</span></h1>
        <p>Find the right community for your lifestyle and budget</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="bv-page-intro bv-page-intro--centered">Bulverde offers a range of neighborhoods — from master-planned communities with full amenities to quiet subdivisions on larger lots. All are served by Comal ISD and share the area's Hill Country character.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Neighborhoods -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Bulverde <span class="accent">Communities</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/bv-indian-springs.png" alt="Estates at Indian Springs homes" class="bv-hood__img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Estates at Indian Springs</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$400K - $700K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>A tranquil, family-oriented gated community nestled in the Hill Country, Estates at Indian Springs offers a quiet atmosphere with beautiful views and deep 80-foot wide lots lined with mature oak trees. Residents enjoy an amenity center, pool, playgrounds, and green belts with walking trails. This is a great fit for buyers looking for space, privacy, and a true Hill Country setting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/bv-bulverde-village.png" alt="Bulverde Village homes" class="bv-hood__img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Bulverde Village</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$350K - $550K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Bulverde Village offers a serene suburban lifestyle with genuine Hill Country charm, featuring mature oak-lined streets and rolling terrain throughout the community. Amenities include a community park with walking and jogging paths, basketball and sand volleyball courts, playgrounds, a splash pad, a luxurious clubhouse, and a pool. The peaceful, friendly atmosphere makes it a popular choice for families looking for convenience near schools and local services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/bv-hidden-trails.png" alt="Hidden Trails homes" class="bv-hood__img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Hidden Trails</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$200K - $400K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Hidden Trails is a master-planned community offering a relaxed, family-oriented lifestyle with resort-level amenities including multiple swimming pools (infinity-edge, beach-entry, and Junior Olympic), a 24/7 fitness center, clubhouse, playgrounds, basketball courts, and a catch-and-release fishing pond. An extensive trail network provides options for walking, hiking, and biking. It is a solid option for first-time buyers and families looking for value in the Bulverde area without sacrificing amenities or the Hill Country lifestyle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/bv-johnson-ranch.png" alt="Johnson Ranch homes" class="bv-hood__img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Johnson Ranch</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$350K - $600K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>A distinctive master-planned community spanning 767 acres, with one-third dedicated to natural open space, Johnson Ranch features scenic views, mature oak trees, and extensive trails throughout. Ten distinct neighborhoods offer various home sizes and lot options, from standard to estate-sized properties. This community attracts families and move-up buyers who want built-in lifestyle features and a strong sense of community.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bv-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/bv-singing-hills.png" alt="Singing Hills homes" class="bv-hood__img" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Singing Hills</h3>
          <div class="bv-area__meta">
            <span class="bv-area__price">$300K - $500K</span>
            <span class="bv-area__district">Comal ISD</span>
          </div>
          <p>Also known as The Preserve at Singing Hills, this serene, family-friendly community in the Bulverde/Spring Branch area features rolling hills and lush greenery throughout. Residents enjoy convenient access to the Guadalupe River and Canyon Lake, with homes typically offering 3 to 5 bedrooms. The peaceful setting and natural scenery make Singing Hills a popular choice for buyers who prioritize a quieter pace of life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- School District -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>School <span class="accent">District</span></h2>
          <p>Bulverde is served by one of the top districts in the Hill Country</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bv-schools__grid">
          <a href="https://www.comalisd.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="bv-schools__card">
            <h3>Comal ISD</h3>
            <p>One of the fastest-growing districts in Texas, Comal ISD serves the entire Bulverde area. The district is known for strong academics, modern facilities, and a wide range of extracurricular programs.</p>
            <span class="bv-schools__link">Visit Comal ISD Website →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section" style="background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Help <span class="accent">Narrowing It Down</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">I can walk you through the differences between Bulverde communities and help you focus your search on neighborhoods that match your priorities.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get Help Narrowing Down Areas</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ParallaxBanner image="/images/generated/comal-river.png" />

  <ContactForm context="I need help narrowing down Bulverde neighborhoods..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .bv-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: url('/images/generated/home-nb-modern.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .bv-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }

  .bv-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .bv-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bv-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 0.3rem;
  }

  .bv-page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .bv-page-intro--centered {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Area Cards */
  .bv-area {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bv-hood__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .bv-area h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .bv-area__meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .bv-area__price {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .bv-area__district {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .bv-area p {
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .bv-area p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Schools */
  .bv-schools__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bv-schools__card {
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bv-schools__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .bv-schools__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .bv-schools__card:hover h3 {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .bv-schools__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bv-schools__link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bv-area__meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
